      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but finals week is coming up and i'm feeling super low and unmotivated. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help with my mood. since its just a natural herbal stuff, is it cool to take it with my prescription? or will it mess anything up?",
